snippet.title: TLP #39 The Bench Players In Professional Sports
snippet.description:
In this Episode of The Lama Podcast, we speak on how Jered's Mom would avoid an assault, Her Jokes, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, Dr. Dre and his divorce. We also laughed at the thought of the losers in professional sports, the lengths greats will go to win, and the Patriot Dynasty, Who was behind it? all this and more, strap in, It's The Lama Podcast.
